1 Cor. 1.30. Of him are ye in Chriſt Jeſus who of God is made unto us Wiſdoms, Righteouſneſs, Sanctification and Redemption, that is, All. Thus all Beleevers are perfect here, to wit, as they are in Chriſt; becauſe they have a fulneſs laid up in him, of all things needfull for ſalvation, though they receive thereof but by degrees, according to their Neceſſity, Capacity, and Aptitude. Therefore they are all imperfect in themſelves, while they live here below.

